Article finder ruby app.. just for fun

start the program by launching the init.rb from terminal
Some current functionalities are: 
Adding article, listing articles, serach for articles by author/publication name or by date etc.
Sorting results is also possible. 

                                     LISTING ARTICLES                                               

 Title                     Author             Publication                    Date      
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 XYZ                       XYZ                   XYZ                         2013      
 XYZ                       XYZ                   XYZ                         2015      
 XYZ                       XYZ                   XYZ                         2014          
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sort using: 'list title/author/publication/date' or 'list by title/author/publication/date'


